Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,替我向莎拉问好\N{\rEng}Give Sarah my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,多处撕裂伤\N{\rEng}...multiple lacerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我女儿 她才五岁\N{\rEng}My daughter, she's five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 这里是医院\N{\rEng}It's okay. You're in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上痛吗\N{\rEng}Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以给你注射止痛药\N{\rEng}We can give you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 艾莉 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 艾莉\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}最后生还者\N第二季 第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,(三个月后)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一到十级 你的疼痛有几级\N{\rEng}And how would you rate your pain? Scale of one to ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼 零级\N{\rEng}Nothing. Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,零级 已经很好了\N{\rEng}Zero. Can't ask for much more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 最后一次肺功能检查\N{\rEng}Okay. One last PFT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rEng}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不错\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 就是今天了\N{\rEng}Alright. Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那我可以... - 就快了\N{\rEng}- So, can I just-- - Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你还得见一个人 然后就能出院了\N{\rEng}I just need you to see one more person, then you're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷\N{\rEng}Oh, for fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗  - 挺好的\N{\rEng}- How are you doing? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回答这么快就是不好的表现\N{\rEng}If you say it that fast, it kind of implies you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 再问我一遍\N{\rEng}Okay, ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 你好吗\N{\rEng}How are you doing, Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想 这事很复杂 毕竟感觉这东西...\N{\rEng}Give me a moment. It's really complicated 'cause, you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我一直被困在这里 自从...\N{\rEng}Oh, come on, man, I've been stuck in here since...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我想他 他对我来说很重要 我既伤心又难过\N{\rEng}Yeah, I miss him. He meant a lot to me. So, yeah. Upset and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEng}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好奇的是跨年夜的事\N{\rEng}But I was actually wondering about New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个在舞会上吵架了 那是你最后一次和他说话吗\N{\rEng}You two got into it at the dance. Was that the last time you spoke to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家时 他站在门廊上\N{\rEng}When I got home, he was on the porch,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我该跟他聊聊的 但我没有\N{\rEng}and I should've talked to him, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你后悔吗  - 当然后悔\N{\rEng}- Do you regret that? - Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你和一个人最后相处的时光\N{\rEng}But your final moment with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不能定义你们整体的关系\N{\rEng}doesn't define your whole time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,道理是这个道理 但事实往往如此\N{\rEng}It shouldn't, but it often does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在我和乔尔相处的最后时光里 他曾说...\N{\rEng}In my last moment with Joel, he said he
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他对不起你\N{\rEng}wronged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能很严重\N{\rEng}Maybe bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他干什么了吗\N{\rEng}What is it that he said that he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,问题就在这儿 他的话前后不搭\N{\rEng}Well, that's the thing. It didn't really make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说“我救了她”\N{\rEng}He said, "I saved her."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他救过我很多次\N{\rEng}He saved me a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对 换我也会这么想 但那不算“对不起”\N{\rEng}Yeah, I would think so. But that's not wronging someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪\N{\rEng}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他什么意思\N{\rEng}No idea what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我没觉得他对不起我\N{\rEng}I don't feel wronged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他说的是什么 真希望我能放过他\N{\rEng}Man, I wish I could have let him off the hook for whatever it was he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只能放过自己了\N{\rEng}I guess I'll have to let myself off the hook for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好了\N{\rEng}Well, you really are doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\rEng}Shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果人人都像你这么健康 我还怎么换取大麻和酒啊\N{\rEng}if everyone were as healthy as you, what would I do for weed and booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 这镇上还有很多操蛋的人\N{\rEng}I wouldn't worry, Gail, there's still a lot of fucked up people in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对 但你不是\N{\rEng}Yeah. But not you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,(米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(乔尔 谢谢你做的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我去医院了\N{\rEng}I went to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么时候让你出院的\N{\rEng}When'd they let you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 30分钟前 - 很好\N{\rEng}- Thirty minutes ago. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让我见盖尔了\N{\rEng}They made me talk to Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没说...\N{\rEng}I never said--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你来看了我那么多次 我早该说谢谢了\N{\rEng}I should have said thank you for all those times you came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不用客气 换我住院 你也会来看我的\N{\rEng}That's okay. You would have done the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 也许不会那么频繁 - 是啊 可能不会\N{\rEng}- Yeah, maybe not as often. - Yeah, no, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了饼干给你吃\N{\rEng}I made you cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rEng}Just 'cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算是一份和解礼吧\N{\rEng}This is a peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要让你生气了\N{\rEng}Because I'm about to make you angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院里...\N{\rEng}In the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾问过我\N{\rEng}when you asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那天的事...\N{\rEng}about that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我没听到任何有用的信息\N{\rEng}I told you I didn't learn anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我没说实话\N{\rEng}That wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们大部分人的名字 也知道他们是哪里来的\N{\rEng}I know most of their names, and I know where they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说完\N{\rEng}Please, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生叫我不要让你太激动 - 我不在乎\N{\rEng}- The doctors told me not to upset you. - I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我一旦说出他们在哪 你会拔掉输液管\N{\rEng}And I knew that if I told you where they were, you'd just start pulling your tubes out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,爬也要爬过去找他们\N{\rEng}and crawling on your hands and knees to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\rEng}I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你浪费了我们的时间 你让他们逃走了\N{\rEng}You cost us time. You let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,首先\N{\rEng}First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,几个星期以来 这镇上一片狼藉 到处都是葬礼\N{\rEng}this town was wreckage and funerals for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会去追杀任何人\N{\rEng}Nobody was gonna go after anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我突然想到\N{\rEng}And then it occurred to me, if you wanna find someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想找一个人 而你只知道对方最终的目的地...\N{\rEng}and the only thing you know about them is where they're gonna end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如让对方先到了再说\N{\rEng}Maybe let them get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱他\N{\rEng}I loved him too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们先说名字\N{\rEng}Okay, let's start with names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个黑发男叫曼尼 另一个男的叫欧文\N{\rEng}The dark-haired guy was Manny. The other guy was Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,黑发女孩和光头女孩里有一个叫诺拉\N{\rEng}The girl with the dark hair and the bald one, one of them's named Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不确定是哪个 - 那个扎辫子的女孩\N{\rEng}- I'm not sure which. - The girl with the braid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\rEng}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\rEng}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来自什么地方\N{\rEng}Where are they from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在一个背包上看到了一块布章\N{\rEng}I saw a patch on a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,黄色三角 有个狼头...\N{\rEng}Yellow triangle, wolf's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还有三个字母 WLF\N{\rEng}and the letters W-L-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得尤金给我讲过 他还在火萤时的一个故事\N{\rEng}And then, I remembered a story Eugene told me from back when he was a Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有些地区性小团体 都想对抗联邦救灾局\N{\rEng}He said that there were these small regional groups in the West all trying to fight FEDRA,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还说他们没有联合起来真够蠢的\N{\rEng}and how stupid it was that they didn't just join together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个团体就是华盛顿解放阵线\N{\rEng}One of those groups was the Washington Liberation Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来自西雅图\N{\rEng}Out of Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WLF 狼\N{\rEng}W-L-F. Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一群傻逼\N{\rEng}Fucking morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他有说这个团体有多小吗  - 没说\N{\rEng}- Did he say how small they were? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 既然从那以后没人提过他们\N{\rEng}But seeing as how no one's ever mentioned them since,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜应该是我们能应付的小团体\N{\rEng}I'm guessing small enough for us to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谁知道这事\N{\rEng}Who else knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们俩\N{\rEng}Just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我没打算在告诉你之前告诉任何人\N{\rEng}I wasn't gonna tell anyone before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\rEng}So, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\rEng}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我得考虑一下\N{\rEng}I gotta think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑什么 我们去干掉那些家伙\N{\rEng}Think about what? Let's fucking get these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉 事情没那么简单\N{\rEng}Ellie, it ain't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小镇还在恢复中 你也一样\N{\rEng}The town is still recovering. So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们明白你的出发点 - 不 我们不明白\N{\rEng}- We get where you're coming from-- - No, we don't get where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 如果死的人是你 乔尔早在天亮前就赶往西雅图了\N{\rEng}I don't get where you're coming from. If it had been you, Joel would be halfway to Seattle before the sun came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么做一定是为了救我的命\N{\rEng}He'd be halfway to Seattle to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可我们现在有伤亡 还不能走\N{\rEng}But when we lost people, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,换他也会崩溃的 他会把一切责任揽到自己身上\N{\rEng}It would just break him like it was his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过很多次了 别以为我不了解他\N{\rEng}I saw that time and time again. And don't talk to me like I didn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥\N{\rEng}He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我不是说你不该去\N{\rEng}Listen, I'm not sayin' you shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然要组队 就得组一支像样的队伍\N{\rEng}But if we're gonna put a posse together, we gotta do it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把这件事告诉玛丽亚 没错 必须告诉她\N{\rEng}which means taking it to Maria. Yes, it's fuckin' necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她会召开议会 通知全镇\N{\rEng}She's gonna want a council meeting, open it up to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,每个想发声的人都能发声\N{\rEng}Everyone who wants to get heard gets heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你会支持我们的 对吧\N{\rEng}But you'll back us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEng}Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\rEng}And you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再有事瞒着我 就去最累的岗位上待一个月\N{\rEng}you hold out information on me again, you got rendering detail for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 艾莉...\N{\rEng}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把死者埋在镇南十英里的地方了\N{\rEng}We buried our dead ten miles south of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去看他\N{\rEng}If you want to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅图的时候再去吧\N{\rEng}When we're on our way to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(普吉特步道 植物园 西雅图步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\rEng}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没人跟来 很安全 继续前进\N{\rEng}"No one following. All clear. Keep moving."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们重新安顿好 我们会教你吹口哨的\N{\rEng}Once we get resettled, I'll teach you to whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不能告诉我目的地是哪里\N{\rEng}Why can't you tell me where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们还不知道\N{\rEng}'Cause we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经说了我们要去的原因\N{\rEng}I've told you the reason we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但她为什么不能保护我们\N{\rEng}I know, but why can't she just keep us safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,先知\N{\rEng}The Prophet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她十年前就死了 康斯坦丝 我可不会指望她帮我们\N{\rEng}She's been dead ten years, Constance. I wouldn't count on her to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但艾斯拉说先知是永生的\N{\rEng}But Ezra said the Prophet is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从某种角度看没错\N{\rEng}Well, she is, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但先知不是魔法\N{\rEng}A prophet isn't magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是...\N{\rEng}They're just
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到别人看不到的真相\N{\rEng}people that see truths hidden from others
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,并且不计代价分享真相的人\N{\rEng}and share that truth, no matter what the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的先知也是如此\N{\rEng}So it was with our Prophet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 没错\N{\rEng}So it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是这样让她的精神永存的\N{\rEng}That's how we keep her spirit alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,遵循她的话语 服从她的教诲 同时保护自己的安全\N{\rEng}Follow her words, we obey her teachings, but we keep ourselves safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那能给我一把锤子吗\N{\rEng}Then, can I have a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你觉得更安全了吗\N{\rEng}Tell me, you feel safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 我们现在给你的东西\N{\rEng}Understand, what we're giving you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,会比锤子给你更多的安全感\N{\rEng}will keep you far, far safer than a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是出离\N{\rEng}Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,出离家乡\N{\rEng}From home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,出离战争\N{\rEng}From war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,找掩护 快\N{\rEng}Take cover! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是恶魔吗\N{\rEng}Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是狼\N{\rEng}Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 注意旋转 再来\N{\rEng}Alright. Good, but rotate. More.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在换右边 只打右边\N{\rEng}Now, the right side. Just the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这边伤害更大 - 我注意到了\N{\rEng}- Come on, man, that side hurts more. - I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 - 好\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用力点 坚持住 最后五拳\N{\rEng}Harder. Harder! Let's go! Last five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 今天到此为止 - 好\N{\rEng}- There it is, okay. Done for the day. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\rEng}So, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一个无所事事三个月的人能做成这样\N{\rEng}Well, for someone who sat on their ass for three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得很惊喜 - 是吗\N{\rEng}- I'm pleasantly surprised. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,平时做俯卧撑了\N{\rEng}Push-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对 还在他们不注意时卷腹了\N{\rEng}Yeah, and crunches when they weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了 再过几周 你就能恢复原来的状态\N{\rEng}Yeah, that'll do it. A few more weeks, and you'll be right back to where you were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.73,0:24:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也就是你该有的水平的八成 - 随便了 去你的\N{\rEng}- Which is 80% of where you should have been. - Whatever. Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你加入议会了\N{\rEng}So, I heard you're on the council now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那你肯定知道接下来的会议\N{\rEng}So, you know about the meeting coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.79,0:24:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我知道\N{\rEng}I know about the meeting coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.25,0:24:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我能指望你吗\N{\rEng}Can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能讨论即将开始的投票\N{\rEng}I can't discuss upcoming votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.88,0:24:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞什么 是我啊 - 我知道\N{\rEng}- Seriously? It's me. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.26,0:24:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 当时你也在场\N{\rEng}Dude, you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这我也知道\N{\rEng}I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.43,0:24:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\rEng}Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.14,0:24:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,听完大家的意见 议会才能作决定\N{\rEng}The council won't make up their mind until we hear people speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.98,0:24:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我给你一点建议\N{\rEng}So, here's a little advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.11,0:25:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的想法整理清楚 写下来 明天念给大家听\N{\rEng}Organize your thoughts, write them down, and then read 'em out loud tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.11,0:25:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道了 因为我很蠢 - 因为你愤怒 艾莉\N{\rEng}- Okay, yeah, 'cause I'm stupid. - 'Cause you're angry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会投票给愤怒的人\N{\rEng}And no one's gonna vote for angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...所以我一直说我们要多投资火鸡\N{\rEng}Which is why I keep saying we need to invest more in turkeys
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.59,0:25:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,少投资鸡\N{\rEng}and less in chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.92,0:25:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这就要说回我之前对玉米的看法了\N{\rEng}And that brings me back to my earlier point about corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.39,0:25:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人听我这么说过 玉米不是最容易种植的作物\N{\rEng}Corn, some of you have heard me say, is not the easiest crop to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.18,0:25:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但它是生长最快的作物之一\N{\rEng}but it is among the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.31,0:25:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以绘一张图 把收成时间和所需资源以及难易度...\N{\rEng}You can plot a graph that shows ease and resources versus time to harvest and get a li--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.94,0:25:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特 抱歉打断你 不要偏题\N{\rEng}Scott, I'm sorry, but we gotta keep you on target here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.82,0:25:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是公开会议 章程上说...\N{\rEng}But it's an open meeting. The bylaws say that--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我们应该回到 大家原本要讨论的议程上来\N{\rEng}Maybe we should stick to what everyone else came here to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.82,0:25:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我对西雅图的事没意见\N{\rEng}I don't really have an opinion on the Seattle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,斯考特说完了 接下来是瑞秋\N{\rEng}So, that was Scott. Next is Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要...\N{\rEng}Yeah, Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见 大声点\N{\rEng}Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能帮我抱着他吗  - 好\N{\rEng}- Can you take him, please? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.38,0:26:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.77,0:26:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说乔尔对我们很多人来说非常重要\N{\rEng}I said that Joel meant so much to so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.90,0:26:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但他并非唯一一个重要的人\N{\rEng}But he wasn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.15,0:26:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我失去了我妹妹\N{\rEng}I lost my sister that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.98,0:26:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很多人都埋葬了家人\N{\rEng}A lot of people in here buried family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.32,0:26:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们要派去16个顶尖成员\N{\rEng}And now, you wanna send, what, you're saying 16 of our best?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.57,0:26:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不在的时候 如果掠夺者来了 谁去墙上抵御他们\N{\rEng}Well, while they're gone, who's gonna be on the wall if Raiders come?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,墙还没修好呢\N{\rEng}A wall that's barely mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.79,0:26:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而且谁也不能保证 那16个人都能回来\N{\rEng}And none of you up there can promise us that all 16 will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我同情你们 汤米和艾莉\N{\rEng}So, my heart is with you, Tommy and Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们伤亡惨重 现在出击太早了\N{\rEng}We are too hurt, and it is too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.13,0:26:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 瑞秋\N{\rEng}Thank you, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.72,0:26:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位是卡莱尔\N{\rEng}Next is Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.60,0:27:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我长话短说 毕竟这是个简单的决定\N{\rEng}I'll be quick. 'Cause this one's simple to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.77,0:27:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来我们这里\N{\rEng}People came
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.94,0:27:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了乔尔\N{\rEng}and killed Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.90,0:27:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不想复仇\N{\rEng}So, why wouldn't we wanna take our vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.20,0:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们不该那么做\N{\rEng}Well, because we're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宽恕他人 方能被人宽恕\N{\rEng}Forgive and be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.12,0:27:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,放下怨恨和仇恨\N{\rEng}No grudges. No revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.25,0:27:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不是基督徒 可我一直觉得这么做很明智\N{\rEng}And I'm not even a Christian. I've always seen the wisdom in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.71,0:27:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是我们与掠夺者和杀人犯 不同的地方\N{\rEng}That's what separates us from the Raiders and the murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.09,0:27:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们懂得仁慈\N{\rEng}Our capacity for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那些混蛋不配得到我们的仁慈\N{\rEng}Those sons of bitches don't deserve our mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.52,0:27:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不配 所以才叫仁慈啊\N{\rEng}Well, of course they don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的屁话\N{\rEng}That's what makes it mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.23,0:27:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能这么说 也不是什么好东西\N{\rEng}Well, to hell with that. And to hell with you for saying it, Carlisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.23,0:27:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赛斯 坐下 - 不\N{\rEng}- Seth, sit down. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不在发言名单上 - 不\N{\rEng}- You're not on the list. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.40,0:27:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在说什么\N{\rEng}What the hell are we all talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.61,0:27:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦 太不公平了\N{\rEng}It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.07,0:27:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要原谅每一个 骑在我们头上拉屎的人吗\N{\rEng}What, we gotta forgive everybody when they show up and piss in our eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.16,0:27:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们闯进了我们家\N{\rEng}They came into our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.54,0:28:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抓走了我们的人\N{\rEng}They took one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.04,0:28:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEng}My God,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.25,0:28:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有人射杀了你们的兄弟 你们还想把门锁拆了\N{\rEng}somebody shoots your brother, you wanna take the locks off your doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.63,0:28:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,幼稚\N{\rEng}Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.59,0:28:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些白痴 他们还会回来的\N{\rEng}You idiots, they'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.55,0:28:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们没让他们付出代价\N{\rEng}They'll come back because we didn't make 'em pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.89,0:28:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等他们回来时 一定带着嘲笑的嘴脸\N{\rEng}And when they come back, they'll be laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.52,0:28:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们都活该\N{\rEng}And you'll all deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.52,0:28:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群...\N{\rEng}Bunch of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的受害者\N{\rEng}goddamn victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.16,0:28:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(斯考特 瑞秋 卡莱尔 艾莉)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.46,0:28:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,“我通常不会准备发言稿”\N{\rEng}I normally don't write things down
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.27,0:29:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“因为我向来有话直说 不假思索”\N{\rEng}because I normally don't think before I talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“这让我惹上了不少麻烦”\N{\rEng}which has gotten me in trouble before, a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.86,0:29:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“让我付出了无法挽回的代价”\N{\rEng}and it's cost me in ways that sometimes couldn't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.95,0:29:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我这次输不起 因为我知道我的要求很过分”\N{\rEng}But I can't afford that right now, because I know what I'm asking is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.24,0:29:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要我们在最糟的时机”\N{\rEng}I'm asking us to risk more people and resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“拿更多的人力和资源去冒险”\N{\rEng}and at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.37,0:29:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“我想告诉大家 我想要的并非复仇”\N{\rEng}And I want everyone to know, it's not because I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,“真的 这跟复仇无关”\N{\rEng}It's not. It's not about revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.92,0:29:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要的是 你们过去给予他人的东西”\N{\rEng}What I want is what you used to give people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.68,0:29:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,“我要正义”\N{\rEng}I want justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.55,0:29:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,“因为除此之外 就只剩沉默与放弃了”\N{\rEng}Because it's either that, or we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.14,0:29:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“而外面的人 也只会默默地放弃我们”\N{\rEng}That's what everyone else out there is going to do for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.52,0:29:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“如果我或你们遭遇不幸”\N{\rEng}Nothing. A whole world of people who won't lift a finger
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“全世界没有人愿意动一动手指”\N{\rEng}if something bad happens to me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.69,0:29:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们有专门的词称呼这种人”\N{\rEng}We have a word for these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,“那就是‘陌生人’”\N{\rEng}They're called strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“我觉得我们之间不是陌生人”\N{\rEng}Well, I don't think that we're strangers to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.03,0:30:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“我得知道我能依靠你们”\N{\rEng}And I want to know that I can count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.58,0:30:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“我发誓 如果有人伤害你们或你们爱的人”\N{\rEng}And I swear, if someone hurts any of you or the people you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.50,0:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,“你们也可以依靠我”\N{\rEng}you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.63,0:30:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“这才是我们的凝聚力”\N{\rEng}That's what holds all this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.25,0:30:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是聚餐 也不是跨年舞会”\N{\rEng}Not potluck dinners or New Year's Eve dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.17,0:30:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“更不是一堵墙 因为那堵墙已经被撞破了”\N{\rEng}Definitely not a wall, because that thing got busted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.14,0:30:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“而杰克逊依然挺立”\N{\rEng}But Jackson is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.31,0:30:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“我会接受议会的一切决议”\N{\rEng}I'll accept whatever the council decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.48,0:30:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“但我拜托你们”\N{\rEng}But I am asking you, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.81,0:30:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“不惜一切代价伸张正义”\N{\rEng}do what it takes to see that justice is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.28,0:30:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“不是为了我”\N{\rEng}Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.36,0:30:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,“甚至不是为了乔尔”\N{\rEng}Not even for Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.74,0:30:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“我拜托你们为我们大家这么做”\N{\rEng}I am asking you, please, do it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.79,0:30:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.38,0:31:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,议会将就派遣16名成员前往西雅图\N{\rEng}The council will now vote on the proposal to send a party of 16 citizens to Seattle
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.43,0:31:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找并处决杀害乔尔之人的提案 进行投票\N{\rEng}to find the people who killed Joel and execute them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.37,0:31:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米贝丝\N{\rEng}Amy-Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.17,0:31:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,“赞成”\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.22,0:31:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.93,0:31:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“赞成”\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.47,0:31:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.73,0:31:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“赞成”\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.61,0:31:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.94,0:31:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.36,0:31:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.91,0:32:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.99,0:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“反对”\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.12,0:32:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,八票反对 三票赞成 提案被否决了\N{\rEng}The vote is 8 to 3. The proposal is rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.59,0:32:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,休庭\N{\rEng}Adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.28,0:32:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 九号球员\N{\rEng}Here we go, nine. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.62,0:32:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 盯紧球  - 快\N{\rEng}Grab the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.04,0:32:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好样的 九号  - 加油 罗德尼 冲啊\N{\rEng}Attaboy, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.04,0:32:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死 - 他没事\N{\rEng}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.88,0:32:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你是球迷\N{\rEng}I didn't know you were a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.34,0:33:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我当年可买过老虎队的季票呢\N{\rEng}Hell, yeah! I had Tigers season tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.47,0:33:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这其实跟2003年的球队差不多\N{\rEng}This actually isn't that far off from the '03 squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.51,0:33:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝啤酒吗 我跟马歇尔拿的\N{\rEng}You want a beer? I get them from Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.53,0:33:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开会时 我在人群中看到你了\N{\rEng}I spotted you in the crowd at the meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.41,0:33:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.58,0:33:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我心想\N{\rEng}And I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.95,0:33:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“她过去几周可能特别忙”\N{\rEng}she's probably been extra busy these last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.37,0:33:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太残忍了\N{\rEng}Brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.88,0:33:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都该去看心理医生 消化发生的一切\N{\rEng}And I'm supposed to see a shrink myself, you know, to process it all, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.13,0:33:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可这里没有别人了\N{\rEng}I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.76,0:33:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你怎么办  - 我是个酒鬼\N{\rEng}- So, what do you do, then? - Oh, well, I'm an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.26,0:33:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我尽可能地多抽大麻\N{\rEng}And I smoke as much weed as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.64,0:33:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一场大灾难\N{\rEng}You know, complete fuckin' disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.27,0:33:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但你来找我不是因为担心我\N{\rEng}But you're not here 'cause you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.02,0:33:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,两人出局了 各位 加油\N{\rEng}Two outs, guys, two outs. Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.65,0:33:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到别人看不到的东西\N{\rEng}You see things that others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.15,0:34:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心她会做傻事\N{\rEng}I'm nervous she's gonna do somethin' stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.99,0:34:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 你不相信她的发言  - 你相信吗\N{\rEng}- What, you didn't believe her speech? - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.78,0:34:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不信 她是个骗子\N{\rEng}Course not. She's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.29,0:34:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,撒谎的人不一定是骗子\N{\rEng}Well, there's a difference between lyin' and being a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.75,0:34:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 她就是骗子\N{\rEng}Oh, I know. And that one? Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.04,0:34:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能只跟一个人说过实话 而他已经...\N{\rEng}There was maybe one person she told the truth to, and he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.76,0:34:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们可以在这一点上各持己见\N{\rEng}But we can agree to disagree about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.22,0:34:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是你很害怕 那我们谈谈吧\N{\rEng}What matters is you're afraid. So, let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.10,0:34:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不收钱\N{\rEng}Okay. Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.19,0:34:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想看她步乔尔的后尘\N{\rEng}I just don't want her to go down the same paths that Joel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.32,0:34:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他满口的正当理由\N{\rEng}Comin' up with justifications and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.82,0:34:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,其实只是在宣泄而已\N{\rEng}All he was really doin' was lashin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.87,0:34:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她的行为可能是跟他学的\N{\rEng}So, you think she might have learned that behavior from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.54,0:35:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其实后天教养的作用微乎其微 其余的都是天性\N{\rEng}Turns out nurture can only do this much. The rest is nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.55,0:35:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她走上某条路 那也不是乔尔教她的\N{\rEng}If she's on a path, it's not one that Joel put her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.47,0:35:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rEng}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.09,0:35:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们一开始就是并肩而行\N{\rEng}I think they were walking side by side from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.93,0:35:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米 我明白\N{\rEng}Tommy, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她归你管了 你想帮她避开麻烦\N{\rEng}You inherited her, and you wanna keep her out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.23,0:35:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作为从业40年的心理医生 我劝你一句\N{\rEng}Take it from a psychotherapist of 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.94,0:35:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人...\N{\rEng}Some people just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.49,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人无法拯救\N{\rEng}Some people just can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.27,0:36:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁  - 迪娜\N{\rEng}- Who is it? - Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.52,0:36:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你好\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.99,0:36:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要睡了\N{\rEng}I'm just going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.86,0:36:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\rEng}No, I don't think that is where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.50,0:36:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一个人吗\N{\rEng}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.37,0:36:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.84,0:36:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\rEng}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.68,0:36:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rEng}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.81,0:36:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别劝我放弃 - 你以为我是来劝你的\N{\rEng}- Please don't try and talk me out of this. - You think that's why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.89,0:36:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说说你的计划吧\N{\rEng}So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.19,0:36:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去西雅图杀死艾比\N{\rEng}Go to Seattle and kill Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.23,0:36:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,路线呢\N{\rEng}What route?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.94,0:36:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,西北方\N{\rEng}Northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面都是枪吗 有没有医疗用品\N{\rEng}And is that all guns, or do you have medical supplies in there? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.99,0:36:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好别在你规划好的西北路线上\N{\rEng}Well, better not land weird on an ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.58,0:37:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,崴了脚或发高烧\N{\rEng}or get a fever on your well-charted path "northwest."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.08,0:37:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我该怎么办\N{\rEng}Okay, so what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,远离高速 避开城市或聚落\N{\rEng}Stay off the highways. Steer clear of cities or settlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,第一阶段是穿越国家森林\N{\rEng}First stage is through the national forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.68,0:37:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,出来后 我们沿蛇河峡谷前进\N{\rEng}Once we're out, we follow the Snake River Canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.01,0:37:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后穿越斯诺夸尔米山口 - 斯诺夸尔米\N{\rEng}- then break off through the Snoqualmie Pass. - Snoqualmie?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.98,0:37:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对 斯诺夸尔米\N{\rEng}Yeah. Snoqualmie.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.52,0:37:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从东边接近西雅图 然后根据情况重新做评估\N{\rEng}Approach Seattle from the east, then reassess based on what we find.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.90,0:37:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带好粮食 轻装上路 但要聪明\N{\rEng}Provisions. Travel light, but smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.65,0:37:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拿厚外套当床垫 拿夹克当被子\N{\rEng}Winter coats for beds, jackets for blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.70,0:37:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,急救箱 电池和防熊喷雾都带上 你要带什么手枪\N{\rEng}First aid kits, batteries, bear spray. Now, handguns. What are you bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.16,0:37:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是乔尔的吗\N{\rEng}Is that Joel's?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.37,0:37:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算用这个杀死她\N{\rEng}So, that's what you're gonna kill her with?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.29,0:37:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 那就留到那时候再用\N{\rEng}- Fuckin' right. - Then, save it for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.38,0:37:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它的速度很慢 后坐力特别强\N{\rEng}It's slow and kicks like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.17,0:37:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 你想轰掉你的屁股\N{\rEng}Really? Shoot your damn ass off?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.63,0:37:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人这么劝过我\N{\rEng}I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.26,0:37:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每人起码得有一百发子弹 加上五十发步枪子弹\N{\rEng}We'll want at least 100 shells apiece, plus 50 rifle rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.93,0:38:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你想带什么长枪都可以 只要有瞄准镜就行\N{\rEng}Bring any long gun you want, as long as it's scoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.43,0:38:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,氯片 平底锅 还有帮闪闪保持干燥的东西\N{\rEng}Chlorine tablets, a pan, and something to keep Shimmer dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.31,0:38:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只带闪闪吗  - 对\N{\rEng}- Just Shimmer? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.98,0:38:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们共骑一匹马 减少资源\N{\rEng}We share a horse. Fewer resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.81,0:38:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,其他东西都跟你想的一样 除了这个\N{\rEng}Everything else is what you'd figure, except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.78,0:38:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,靴子\N{\rEng}Boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这双匡威 也尊重你一贯的风格\N{\rEng}Love the Converse. Respect your consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.45,0:38:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能穿帆布鞋横穿荒野\N{\rEng}But you're not crossing open country in fuckin' Chucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.66,0:38:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我那么做过 - 不能穿帆布鞋 有问题吗\N{\rEng}- I've done it before. - No Chucks. Questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.04,0:38:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个 我们怎么弄到那么多东西\N{\rEng}Yeah, one. How the fuck are we gonna get all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.66,0:38:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识一个人\N{\rEng}I know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.83,0:38:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你不会告诉杰西了吧\N{\rEng}Oh, no. No, don't tell me you told Jesse, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.71,0:38:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怀俄明队长 没有\N{\rEng}Captain Wyoming? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.92,0:38:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢他 但他是个死守规矩的人\N{\rEng}I love the man, but he's a little uptight about rules and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.84,0:38:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把你要带的衣服都穿上 口袋里装满子弹\N{\rEng}Wear all the clothes you're gonna bring, fill your pockets with ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其他东西必须装进枪套或背包里\N{\rEng}Everything else needs to fit inside a holster or your backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.22,0:38:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凌晨三点在原来的东门见\N{\rEng}We'll meet by the old east gate, 3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.89,0:38:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨三点\N{\rEng}3:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.65,0:38:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.86,0:38:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.49,0:38:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你可以直接问我的\N{\rEng}You know, you could have just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.45,0:38:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你愿意\N{\rEng}No, I actually didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.74,0:39:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了\N{\rEng}Now you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.95,0:39:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我换\N{\rEng}Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.08,0:39:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这把枪更好 跟我换\N{\rEng}It's better. Trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.31,0:40:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么把它弄出来的\N{\rEng}How'd you get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.43,0:40:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,珍宁在马厩值夜班 她理解我们想做的事\N{\rEng}Jeanine's night watch at the stables. She's sympathetic to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.69,0:40:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想做的事\N{\rEng}"Our cause"?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.06,0:40:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你在议会上说“我们”的 不是我说的\N{\rEng}You're the one that gave the "us" speech, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.61,0:40:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,马鞍袋里都是我偷藏的东西\N{\rEng}Saddlebags are filled with stuff I had squirreled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.40,0:40:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能吃两周的硬面包 绷带 酒精 药物和电池\N{\rEng}Two weeks' worth of hardtack, bandages, alcohol, meds, batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.99,0:40:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟你们一起去 但我在跨年夜被友军误伤了\N{\rEng}I'd come with you, but I caught some friendly fire on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.49,0:40:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定是友军吗  - 天啊\N{\rEng}- You sure it was friendly? - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.16,0:40:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在巡逻队经过之前 你们只有十分钟 快走吧\N{\rEng}We got ten minutes before a patrol comes by. Let's get you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.07,0:42:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(乔尔米勒)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.19,0:44:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 字母F\N{\rEng}Okay, so...F.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.07,0:44:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,字母F 佛...佛利伍麦克乐团\N{\rEng}F. Fleetwood Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.91,0:44:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不对 - 什么\N{\rEng}- Nope. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.29,0:44:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫不对 这是我的看法\N{\rEng}What do you mean, "no"? It's my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.00,0:44:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的看法是错的 因为弗兰克扎帕真的存在\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, your opinion is wrong because Frank Zappa exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.00,0:44:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 字母G\N{\rEng}Okay, so, G.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.21,0:44:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 绿日乐队 - 不 你错了\N{\rEng}- Green Day. - No, you're wrong. It's Guns N' Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.64,0:44:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奥兹奥斯朋\N{\rEng}Ozzy Osbourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.14,0:44:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 分数加倍\N{\rEng}Nice! Double points.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.39,0:45:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,L M N O P\N{\rEng}So, L-M-N-O, P.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.94,0:45:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要让我猜完所有字母吗\N{\rEng}Are you seriously gonna make me do the entire alphabet?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.98,0:45:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我很灵活的 让我想想 换个新话题...\N{\rEng}We don't have to. I'm incredibly flexible. Lemme see, new topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.15,0:45:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沉默也行 - 有了 你杀的第一个人是谁\N{\rEng}- Or silence. - Got one. First person you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.82,0:45:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 真的吗\N{\rEng}Jesus, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.24,0:45:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对 有趣的童年故事\N{\rEng}Yeah, fun stories of childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.20,0:45:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个人死得太离谱 但我可以跟你说说第二个\N{\rEng}Okay, well, the first one's too fucked up, but I can tell you the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.96,0:45:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rEng}I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.75,0:45:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我和乔尔来杰克逊之前的事\N{\rEng}It was a little before Joel and I got to Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.25,0:45:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在堪萨斯城 他被一个没比我大几岁的孩子突袭\N{\rEng}In Kansas City, he got jumped by this kid, maybe just a couple years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.84,0:45:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我从后面接近他 举起枪 然后...就这样\N{\rEng}And I came up behind him, raised my gun and, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.81,0:45:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾莉\N{\rEng}Sorry, Ellie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.85,0:45:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思 杀人的是我 你却替我难过\N{\rEng}Interesting. I shoot a guy, and you feel sorry for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.94,0:45:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么忠诚\N{\rEng}I'm just loyal like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.69,0:45:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你看到露岩或有遮蔽的地方 记得告诉我\N{\rEng}Let me know if you see any outcroppings or spots with cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.74,0:45:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 天气挺好的\N{\rEng}Why? It looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.79,0:46:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 雨来得真快 你怎么知道会这样的\N{\rEng}Holy shit, that came on fast. How the fuck did you know that was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.96,0:46:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是女巫 - 显然是这样\N{\rEng}- I'm a witch. - Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.44,0:46:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.95,0:46:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.55,0:46:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我还有个蠢问题\N{\rEng}Okay, but I have a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.06,0:47:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和跨年夜有关\N{\rEng}It's about New Year's Eve, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.52,0:47:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个吻\N{\rEng}the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.07,0:47:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好 也没什么 你当时嗑嗨了\N{\rEng}Okay. I mean, whatever, you were super high.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.53,0:47:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而你醉了\N{\rEng}And you were drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.11,0:47:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对 所以那不能代表什么 你是想问这个吧\N{\rEng}Right, so it doesn't mean anything, if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.95,0:47:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这个我知道 我想问的是\N{\rEng}No, I know that. My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.71,0:47:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你会给那个吻打几分\N{\rEng}how would you rate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.96,0:47:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一到十分  - 不\N{\rEng}- Scale of one to ten. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.04,0:47:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你以前吻过女孩\N{\rEng}Come on. You've kissed girls before.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.42,0:47:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是同性恋 而我不是\N{\rEng}You're gay, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.59,0:47:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是好奇 我想知道我厉不厉害\N{\rEng}I'm just curious. I wanna know if I'm any good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.26,0:47:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一到十分\N{\rEng}One to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.68,0:47:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 六分\N{\rEng}Okay, fine. Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.39,0:47:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去你的 六分  - 这算不错了\N{\rEng}- Fuck you, "six." - That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.11,0:47:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是烂透了\N{\rEng}That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.86,0:47:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.32,0:47:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,郑重声明一下 我不相信你\N{\rEng}For the record, I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.24,0:48:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你非要问 我就答了 对不起\N{\rEng}Well, you asked, and I told you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.45,0:48:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以回去找杰西\N{\rEng}You can go back to Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.54,0:48:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经找了\N{\rEng}I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.79,0:48:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行了\N{\rEng}Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.09,0:48:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他有没有给你一种悲伤的感觉\N{\rEng}Does he ever strike you as sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.10,0:48:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,杰西吗 有\N{\rEng}Jesse? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.31,0:48:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟你说过原因吗\N{\rEng}Has he ever told you why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.27,0:48:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.52,0:48:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得他内心深处就是悲伤的人\N{\rEng}But I think deep inside, that's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.74,0:48:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至少我希望是这样 - 为什么\N{\rEng}- At least, I hope that's why. - Why would you hope that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.66,0:48:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果不是的话...\N{\rEng}Well, because if it's not that,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.33,0:48:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我的问题了\N{\rEng}then it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.51,0:49:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.47,0:49:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\rEng}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.40,0:49:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉\N{\rEng}Ellie?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.82,0:49:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我没那么嗨\N{\rEng}I wasn't that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.91,0:49:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,(植物园 西雅图步道)
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.71,0:49:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多远\N{\rEng}How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.50,0:49:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很近了\N{\rEng}Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.42,0:49:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大约十英里\N{\rEng}Maybe ten miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.67,0:49:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上 我们会从城北五号公路附近穿出去\N{\rEng}In theory, we'll come out near Highway Five, just north of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.65,0:50:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他死前正在逃跑\N{\rEng}He was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.20,0:50:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么符号\N{\rEng}What's that symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.20,0:50:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 我也是第一次见\N{\rEng}I don't know, I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.59,0:50:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹的口径各不相同 应该不是联邦救灾局干的\N{\rEng}A lot of different calibers. I don't think this was FEDRA.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.72,0:50:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,迪娜\N{\rEng}Dina.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.68,0:50:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,迪娜\N{\rEng}Dina?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.77,0:50:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 那边...\N{\rEng}- You okay? - It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.12,0:51:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\rEng}Doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.67,0:51:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我从没有过这种反应\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm sorry, it's just that's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.71,0:51:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可能是气味太重 - 而且惨不忍睹\N{\rEng}- I think it was the smell. - It wasn't easy to look at either.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.22,0:51:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是他们干的...\N{\rEng}If this was fucking them,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.26,0:51:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果艾比和她的人能对人干出这种事\N{\rEng}if Abby and her crew did this to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.85,0:51:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能杀害孩子...\N{\rEng}to kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.98,0:52:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.03,0:52:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.68,0:52:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很接近了\N{\rEng}We're close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.05,0:53:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(警告 接近监控区 联邦救灾局)
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.92,0:53:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好安静\N{\rEng}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.51,0:53:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对 过于安静了\N{\rEng}Yeah. Too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.30,0:53:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,柯蒂斯还是毒蛇的台词\N{\rEng}Curtis or Viper?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.56,0:53:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都有 他们在四部电影里都说过\N{\rEng}Both, in all four movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.68,0:53:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(西雅图 九英里)
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.81,0:53:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有九英里\N{\rEng}Nine more miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.06,0:53:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,九英里\N{\rEng}Nine more.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.42,0:53:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的西雅图 真漂亮\N{\rEng}Fucking Seattle. Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.89,0:53:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也没人对我们开枪\N{\rEng}Plus, no one's shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.31,0:54:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看来狼也没那么多嘛\N{\rEng}I guess there aren't that many Wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.40,0:54:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要少很多了\N{\rEng}There's about to be a whole lot less.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.77,0:54:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 柯蒂斯还是毒蛇的台词  - 什么\N{\rEng}- Curtis or Viper? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.49,0:54:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是我自创的 我只是想显得我厉害一点\N{\rEng}No, that was just me. I was trying to sound like a badass.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.03,0:54:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来就很厉害\N{\rEng}You don't need to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.76,0:54:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“曼尼”\N{\rEng}Manny.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.35,0:54:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 说吧\N{\rEng}Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.85,0:54:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们要前往前进作战基地 三号和五号检查站之间安全吗 ”\N{\rEng}We're moving up to the FOB. All clear between checkpoint three and five?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.11,0:54:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明明叫我盯着六号和八号 现在又问三号和五号\N{\rEng}Told me to watch six and eight. Now, they want fuckin' three and five.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.28,0:55:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,“曼尼 听到了吗 ”\N{\rEng}Manny, you copy?
